com.ihealth.communication.control

Interface HsProfile


  • public interface HsProfile
    Public APIs for the Hs serials device profiles

    Clients need to call iHealthDevicesManager#registerClient register. When new data from Hs device, The Callback iHealthDevicesCallback#onDeviceNotify can be triggered should call.
